item.title: Other Apps
item.description: Japan travel guides and maps *Japan travel guide All official metro maps for transportation in Tokyo, Osaka, Kyoto, Hakone Introduction of foods you must try in Japan Tips and useful information when you are in Japan to enjoy your days 120% LGBTQ friendly guide *Find travel guides and maps of other countries and cities. https://mytripnavi.com/maps/all/ MyPass app Tired of typing online check-in information over and over again, save your information once and simply copy and paste it from our app for your whole family MyPass-MyID Passport scanner, driving license scanner, ID scanner Quick to fill out flight online check-in by copy and paste from the app Safe to leave your passport in hotel and show the scanned passport image from the app when you are requested to show Easy to manage your card expiration date Could be used in multiple devices Universal Studios Japan - Osaka USJ Guide to Universal Studios Japan Latest map from official USJ site USJ attraction list in your hand Train map and access guide to USJ for first time user One day itinerary for your reference Classic yellow not pad Classic note pad for taking note and memo.
